videos.headline: Jackson doubles Buffalo's lead with 1-yard strike
videos.description: Tyree Jackson pushes his way into the end zone for a short Buffalo touchdown, putting the Bulls up two scores on Kent State.

videos.headline: Osborn's 31-yard catch sets up a third Buffalo TD
videos.description: Tyree Jackson lets a 31-yard pass fly to K.J. Osborn, but he's unable to reach the end zone. On the next drive Emmanuel Reed reaches pay dirt for a 2-yard TD.

videos.headline: Marks finds the open lane and hits pay dirt
videos.description: Kevin Marks rushes for a 5-yard Buffalo touchdown to put the Bulls up 27-0 over Kent State after the PAT is blocked.

videos.headline: Patterson scores his second TD of game
videos.description: Jaret Patterson takes the handoff up the middle to put 6 more on the board for Buffalo against Kent State.
